What is Persona?

Persona is an app, that allows users to generate AI Personas with different AI models.

Users can continue working on Personas by editing the details, expanding information or adding new information, as well as generating the images of Personas.

Users creates Personas in chat like fashion, writing about what to create initially, then writing a comments on what to change, what expand etc.


# Costs and generation restrictions

- Anonymous users, get access to 1 generation per day, without edits or image generation.
- Registered users are rewarded with daily tokens to spend on generation and edits.
- Users can buy tokens, that can be later used to generate personas, edit them or create images. Better models costs more tokens. 